snippet.title: Java Type Casting Tutorial
snippet.description:
New course coming soon! Learn Java Fast launches on July 1st, 2020. Stay informed and join the waitlist: https://course.alexlorenlee.com/courses/learn-java-fast

- This is how you cast a variable in java. ☕

int a = (int) b;

Simply put the type you want it to be in parentheses. That's it! Java will now cast your variable to be the variable type you want.

I hope this helps you with java type casting! This is great practice :)

I hope you enjoyed java type casting tutorial!
